reut2-018.sgm, DOSKOCIL &lt;DOSKD.O> BUYS BACK FIVE PCT OF STOCK, Doskocil Companies Inc said itbought back 310,000 shares or about five pct of its commonstock and its board authorized the repurchase of an additional200,000 common shares.    If completed, the total purchases would represent 8.5 pctof Doskocil's outstanding common stock. Reuter&#3;
